<p>The <b>Rusted Shield</b> (Japanese: <b>くちたたて</b> <i>Rusted Shield</i>) is a <a href="/wiki/Held_item" title="Held item">held item</a> introduced in <a href="/wiki/Generation_VIII" title="Generation VIII">Generation VIII</a>. It is a <a href="/wiki/Category:Legendary_artifacts" title="Category:Legendary artifacts">legendary artifact</a> associated with <a href="/wiki/Zamazenta_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title="Zamazenta (Pokémon)">Zamazenta</a>.
</p>
