<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Effect">Effect</span></h3>
<p>When a <a href="/wiki/Zamazenta_(Pok%C3%A9mon)" title="Zamazenta (Pokémon)">Zamazenta</a> is holding this item in battle, it transforms into its <a href="/wiki/List_of_Pok%C3%A9mon_with_form_differences#Zacian_and_Zamazenta" title="List of Pokémon with form differences">Crowned Shield form</a>. In-battle, it also changes Zamazenta's <a href="/wiki/Iron_Head_(move)" title="Iron Head (move)">Iron Head</a> into <a href="/wiki/Behemoth_Bash_(move)" title="Behemoth Bash (move)">Behemoth Bash</a>.
</p>
